{
  "stem": "12462.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I tried to explore what their thinking was and so forth.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And one evening, I remember a, a gentleman I should mention, by the name of Stuart Herman, who was a student at Strasbourg University, a theological school.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He and I had gone down to Freiburg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we've noticed that one of the young women in the group that was talking to us, maybe four or five people that had gathered around a table, was very quiet.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I arranged, under some pretext or other, to get her off to the side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I said, you seem to be very quiet.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I suspect that you don't want to talk too much in front of these other people.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She says, that's right, and I'm an anti-Nazi, and I always will be.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I have to worry about being thrown in jail.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So that was one kind of experience.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] The Nazis-- the Germans had a couple of students studying in London.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one of them introduced me to his father, who was a director of the [GERMAN] which is the third largest iron  and steel company.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I traveled with her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We both went to Berlin.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We didn't travel together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I met her there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we went to the famous film, [GERMAN], which was a production by Reni, R-E-N-I, Riefenstahl, a famous woman German producer, who produced this film which highly pleased Hitler and the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we saw this film, and there would be applause during the part of it, and so on.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But obviously, that was just part of the propaganda putting on to get control of the minds of ordinary Germans.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I spoke to a British [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] newsman, a journalist, who was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
